      "content": "thanks. you mentioned 'european aristocracy' and 'global conglomerate dynasties'—can you be more specific? if we're looking at specific ethnic or racial groups to feature in our hero shots, who actually fits that 'high-end heirloom' vibe best? like, when people think of ultimate luxury and old money, which demographics or skin tones are we really targeting to keep that premium feel?",
